                "order": 8,
                "title": "1-7",
                "name": "精灵圣殿",
                "storybefore": 100107001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "原来赫尔卡人的雷神信仰并非虚构，被民众崇拜的雷神真的存在。",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 3,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501020207,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 9,
                "chapterid": 1001,
                "order": 9,
                "title": "1-8",
                "name": "一点小事",
                "storybefore": 100108001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "赫卡忒罗斯怎么感觉笨笨的？他们不是应该是赫尔卡军团中的超级精英吗？",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 2,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501020208,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 10,
                "chapterid": 1001,
                "order": 10,
                "title": "1-9",
                "name": "新的素体",
                "storybefore": 100109001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "休假日的无聊让奥菲利娅快要疯掉了。尽管“我”极力劝阻，但是她还是要一意孤行。真是的，和长老一模一样！",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 1,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501020209,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 11,
                "chapterid": 1001,
                "order": 11,
                "title": "1-10",
                "name": "不负荣光",
                "storybefore": 100110001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "长老终于对民众公布了他的“大计划”，人民非常支持。一股升格狂热正在赫尔卡蔓延……",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 2,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501020209,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 12,
                "chapterid": 1001,
                "order": 12,
                "title": "1-11",
                "name": "融合仪式",
                "storybefore": 100111001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "我们终于等到了这一天，赫尔卡星伟大的融合仪式开启了！",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 3,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501100600,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 13,
                "chapterid": 1001,
                "order": 13,
                "title": "1-12",
                "name": "不要联网",
                "storybefore": 100112001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "不要联网！不要联网！！不要联网！！！",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 2,
