                "order": 14,
                "title": "1-13",
                "name": "广播",
                "storybefore": 100113001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "赫尔卡的很多系统都过于陈旧了。而我们付出了相应的代价。",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 1,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501100602,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 15,
                "chapterid": 1001,
                "order": 15,
                "title": "1-14",
                "name": "自救",
                "storybefore": 100114001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "我们不会害怕，不是因为智械的生死观淡薄，而是因为这是正确的事。",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 2,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501100603,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 16,
                "chapterid": 1001,
                "order": 16,
                "title": "1-15",
                "name": "雷神",
                "storybefore": 100115001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "关于雷神与精灵圣殿的秘密，我们还有太多太多的未知……但是雷神不会抛弃我们，他会为赫尔卡献上最后的赐福。",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 3,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501100604,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 17,
                "chapterid": 1001,
                "order": 17,
                "title": "1-16",
                "name": "不死的巨人",
                "storybefore": 100116001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "长老在制造德尔塔II的时候，几乎想到了所有的危险情况并为之添加了应急预案。只是没想到的德尔塔II会有一天站在我们的对立面……",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 2,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501170801,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 18,
                "chapterid": 1001,
                "order": 18,
                "title": "1-17",
                "name": "最后的希望",
                "storybefore": 100117001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "奥菲利娅，我有个计划。只是不知道我顶不顶得住……",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 1,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501170802,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 19,
                "chapterid": 1001,
                "order": 19,
                "title": "1-18",
                "name": "余烬的传承",
                "storybefore": 100118001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "我们胜利了，但是我也付出了惨痛的代价。然而对于文明的存续而言，没有任何的代价会大到难以接受。",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 2,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501170803,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 20,
                "chapterid": 1001,
                "order": 20,
                "title": "1-19",
                "name": "致千年后的你",
                "storybefore": 100119001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "好久不见，奥菲利娅。",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 3,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501170804,
                "open": 1
            },
