                "chapterid": 1002,
                "order": 2,
                "title": "1-2",
                "name": "时空之门",
                "storybefore": 100202001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "我们寻找新的宜居星球的概率太低了，拜伦号的能源并不允许我们做多次尝试。或许时空之门是最好的计划。",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 3,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501241601,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 24,
                "chapterid": 1002,
                "order": 3,
                "title": "1-3",
                "name": "绝望之沼",
                "storybefore": 100203001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "如果这个世界上真的有不可违抗的命运，那么它一定是以折磨自己的拥趸为乐的。宇宙无垠，唯绝望与痛苦永存。",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 2,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501241602,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 25,
                "chapterid": 1002,
                "order": 4,
                "title": "1-4",
                "name": "尤纳斯",
                "storybefore": 100204001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "祂来了，带着物质化的恐惧，降临在拜伦号附近……",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 1,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501241603,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 26,
                "chapterid": 1002,
                "order": 5,
                "title": "1-5",
                "name": "长者的荣耀",
                "storybefore": 100205001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "只剩下我和长老了，频繁的战斗让我筋疲力尽。但是长老说他还有办法。",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 2,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501241604,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 27,
                "chapterid": 1002,
                "order": 6,
                "title": "1-6",
                "name": "凝视深渊",
                "storybefore": 100206001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "我被拉入了祂的领域，被迫直面神明。",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 3,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501241605,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 28,
                "chapterid": 1002,
                "order": 7,
                "title": "1-7",
                "name": "独自前行",
                "storybefore": 100207001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "终于还是走到了这一步，我必须带这个居民的数据硬盘去寻找生机。而长老……",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 2,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501241606,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 29,
                "chapterid": 1002,
                "order": 8,
                "title": "1-8",
                "name": "我是谁",
                "storybefore": 100208001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "病毒的侵蚀意外的解锁了很多高保密性的舱室，我看到了真相。我，是谁？",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 1,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501241607,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 30,
                "chapterid": 1002,
                "order": 9,
                "title": "1-9",
                "name": "光荣的余焰",
                "storybefore": 100209001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "从此，我将奔向命运的幽途，成为赫尔卡人最后的余焰。",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 2,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501241608,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 31,
                "chapterid": 1002,
                "order": 10,
                "title": "1-10",
                "name": "文明之死",
                "storybefore": 100210001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "给一个文明予以死亡对祂来说是如此的轻而易举，但是只要我还有一口气，我就不会屈服。我要让祂付出代价。",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 3,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501241609,
                "open": 1
            },
            {
                "id": 32,
                "chapterid": 1003,
                "order": 1,
                "title": "1-1",
                "name": "一切正常",
                "storybefore": 100301001,
                "storyafter": 0,
                "intro": "奥菲利娅目前看起来是充满活力的，但是派特博士担心，这种“一切正常”才是不正常的。",
                "item": "1_1400152_1;1_1400153_2;1_300697_1",
                "position": 2,
                "stagetype": 0,
                "bossid": 0,
                "NewMsglogId": 2501241700,
                "open": 1
            },
